Tomcat8安裝目錄/usr/local/apache-tomcat-8.0.23
symbolic link是/usr/local/tomcat指向上面的安裝目錄

重要設定檔如下

(設定CATALINA_HOME環境變數)
/etc/profile.d/jdk8_environments.sh 

(有設定一個JNDI connection pool的資源及VirtualHost)
/usr/local/tomcat/conf/server.xml

(設定ResourceLink指向上面的GlobalNamingResources)
/usr/local/tomcat/conf/context.xml

(Tomcat application manager的用戶登入密碼設定)
/usr/local/tomcat/conf/tomcat-users.xml
